{"author":{"id":"8f990dab382a59e0f4235d96491a4ee14dc34d3b7e9de61d8875aadd396af416"},"ops":[{"type":3,"timestamp":1616423057,"nonce":"bso3BoMRCcI7PugAV8BlIw9yl4g=","metadata":{"github-id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDgwNDEwMzQyMA==","github-url":"https://github.com/OPEN-NEXT/OKH-LOSH/issues/79#issuecomment-804103420"},"message":"Sorry for my late response @moedn, understood!\n\nThe Wikifactory API returns several fields when you ask about a license, such as `abreviation` (which should probably be spelled \"abbreviation\"????), `name`, and `title`. The issue is that they are sometimes inconsistent and don't match a real-world license. Some examples of the GraphQL query responses: \n\nNo distinction between the different BSD license variants: \n```\n{\n        \"abreviation\": \"BSD-2-Clause\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://choosealicense.com/licenses/bsd-2-clause/\",\n        \"name\": \"freeBSD\",\n        \"title\": \"FreeBSD License\"\n}\n```\n\nCC BY 4.0 for `abreviation` but CC0 for `name`:\n```\n{\n        \"abreviation\": \"CC-BY-4.0\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://choosealicense.com/licenses/cc-by-4.0/\",\n        \"name\": \"cc0\",\n        \"title\": \"Creative Commons Attribution 4.0\"\n}\n```\n\nNo version number: \n```\n{\n        \"abreviation\": \"CERN OHL\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://www.ohwr.org/projects/cernohl/wiki\",\n        \"name\": \"cernOHL\",\n        \"title\": \"CERN Open Hardware Licence\"\n}\n```\n\nInconsistent version number: \n```\n{\n        \"abreviation\": \"CC-BY-SA-4.0\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://choosealicense.com/licenses/cc-by-sa-4.0/\",\n        \"name\": \"ccbysa3\",\n        \"title\": \"Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0\"\n}\n```\n\nAlso, I don't think any of the fields give SPDX license strings which I think is important.\n\nThe Wikifactory API allows a GraphQL query for the full list of licenses they support, below is the full response. Note that the list is not very comprehensive and has the problems I mentioned: \n\n```\n{\n  \"data\": {\n    \"licenses\": [\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"Permissive\",\n        \"isHeader\": true,\n        \"link\": \"\",\n        \"name\": \"permissive\",\n        \"title\": \"Popular permissive licenses (modifications may be shared without open sourcing)\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"CC-BY-4.0\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://choosealicense.com/licenses/cc-by-4.0/\",\n        \"name\": \"cc0\",\n        \"title\": \"Creative Commons Attribution 4.0\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"CC0-1.0\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://choosealicense.com/licenses/cc0-1.0/\",\n        \"name\": \"unlicense\",\n        \"title\": \"Creative Commons Zero (Public Domain)\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"MIT\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://choosealicense.com/licenses/mit/\",\n        \"name\": \"mit\",\n        \"title\": \"MIT License\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"BSD-2-Clause\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://choosealicense.com/licenses/bsd-2-clause/\",\n        \"name\": \"freeBSD\",\n        \"title\": \"FreeBSD License\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"Copy Left\",\n        \"isHeader\": true,\n        \"link\": \"\",\n        \"name\": \"copyLeft\",\n        \"title\": \"Popular copyleft licenses (derivatives must be licensed under same terms)\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"CC-BY-SA-4.0\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://choosealicense.com/licenses/cc-by-sa-4.0/\",\n        \"name\": \"ccbysa3\",\n        \"title\": \"Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"GPL-3.0\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://choosealicense.com/licenses/gpl-3.0/\",\n        \"name\": \"gnuGPL\",\n        \"title\": \"GNU General Public License 3\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"OHL\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://www.tapr.org/OHL\",\n        \"name\": \"tapr\",\n        \"title\": \"TAPR Open Hardware License\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"abreviation\": \"CERN OHL\",\n        \"isHeader\": false,\n        \"link\": \"http://www.ohwr.org/projects/cernohl/wiki\",\n        \"name\": \"cernOHL\",\n        \"title\": \"CERN Open Hardware Licence\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```","files":null}]}